content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1220.36 - Permission and accompaniment by Port Authority employee required for entry into certain areas

State Regulations

No person shall enter any storage room, cashier's room, or baggage room at the terminal except with permission and then only when
accompanied by an employee of the Port Authority. Notes
